@node Development
@chapter Development
@cindex development
@cindex contributing

This chapter is for developers who want to modify Codebud: run the test
suite, add a new tool, tune the planner prompt, or understand the
conventions used throughout the codebase.

@menu
* Test Suite::                  Running and understanding the tests.
* Code Style::                  Ruff configuration and formatting.
* Adding a Tool::               The five-step tool-addition checklist.
* Tuning the Planner Prompt::   Improving JSON reliability.
